The paper discusses deep learning models and their limitations in classification tasks. It proposes a new paradigm for classification and introduces a novel architecture called the competitive overcomplete output layer (COOL) neural network. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
